--- linux-2.6.15/Documentation/amd76x_pm.txt	1970-01-01 01:00:00.000000000 +0100
+++ linux-2.6.15-jo/Documentation/amd76x_pm.txt	2006-01-10 19:43:56.000000000 +0100
